qas.question: What is the name of the island on which Atlantic City is located?
In what year was Atlantic City incorporated?
What are the names of the two townships that became part of Atlantic City when it was incorporated?

answers.text: Egg Harbor Township and Galloway Township

qas.question: How many other towns share a border with Atlantic City?

answers.text: Absecon, Brigantine, Pleasantville, Ventnor City and West Atlantic City

qas.question: Which coast is Atlantic City located on?
